T1  - On Optimal Instrumental Variables Estimation of Stationary Time Series Models
AU  - West, Kenneth D.
Y1  - 2001/11/01
PY  - 2001
DA  - 2001/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-2354.00145
T2  - International Economic Review
